<i>60 secondes !</i>

107
00:05:03,816 --> 00:05:07,280
<i>59, 58, 57,</i>

108
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:10,790
<i>56, 55, 54...</i>

109
00:05:10,790 --> 00:05:12,726
<i>Soldat Kasher ?</i>

110
00:05:13,142 --> 00:05:14,806
<i>Soldat ?</i>

111
00:05:15,984 --> 00:05:18,205
Il y a un problème, lieutenant ?

112
00:05:18,205 --> 00:05:19,637
Non, mon colonel.

113
00:05:19,829 --> 00:05:21,267
Alors continuez.

114
00:05:21,267 --> 00:05:24,531
Soldat Lasalle,
sortez-le de là.

115
00:05:26,197 --> 00:05:28,179
Rompez !

116
